{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"tool_RAcM0EynSNSrgM5s6HuIp6Pb","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Custom Desktop Pet 自定义桌面宠物 Steam 价格 截图 官网 月夜Crescent\"\n\nSearch results for query: Custom Desktop Pet Steam price Custom Desktop Pet screenshot Custom Desktop Pet official website\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Recommandé - Produits similaires - Custom Desktop Pet-自定义桌面宠物\",\"url\":\"https://store.steampowered.com/recommended/morelike/app/2297040/?l=french&snr=1_300_morelikev2__105\"},{\"title\":\"Recommended - Similar items - Custom Desktop Pet-自定义桌面宠物\",\"url\":\"https://store.steampowered.com/recommended/morelike/app/2297040/?snr=1_300_morelikev2__105\"},{\"title\":\"Empfohlen - Ähnliches - Custom Desktop Pet-自定义桌面宠物\",\"url\":\"https://store.steampowered.com/recommended/morelike/app/2297040/?l=german&snr=1_300_morelikev2__105\"},{\"title\":\"Custom Desktop Pet-自定义桌面宠物\",\"url\":\"https://isthereanydeal.com/steam/app/2297040/\"},{\"title\":\"Desktop Pet Project game revenue and stats on Steam\",\"url\":\"https://games-stats.com/steam/game/desktop-pet-project/\"},{\"title\":\"Desktop Mate on Steam\",\"url\":\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/3301060/Desktop_Mate/\"},{\"title\":\"Custom Desktop Pet-自定义桌面宠物 Products\",\"url\":\"https://isthereanydeal.com/game/custom-desktop-pet-zi-ding-yi-zhuo-mian-chong-wu/products/\"},{\"title\":\"Steam 上的 Custom Desktop Pet-自定义桌面宠物\",\"url\":\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/2297040/_/?l=schinese\"},{\"title\":\"Custom Desktop Pet-自定义桌面宠物 - PCGameBenchmark\",\"url\":\"https://www.pcgamebenchmark.com/custom-desktop-pet-zi-ding-yi-zhuo-mian-chong-wu-system-requirements\"},{\"title\":\"Custom Desktop Pet-自定义桌面宠物 | Steambase\",\"url\":\"https://steambase.io/games/custom-desktop-pet-%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E6%A1%8C%E9%9D%A2%E5%AE%A0%E7%89%A9/info\"},{\"title\":\"Custom Desktop Pet-自定义桌面宠物 | Deku Deals\",\"url\":\"https://www.dekudeals.com/items/custom-desktop-pet\"}]\n\n根据搜索结果，为您整理了 **《Custom Desktop Pet / 自定义桌面宠物》**（开发者：**月夜Crescent**）的相关信息：\n\n## 1. Steam 页面与价格\n- **App ID**：2297040\n- **Steam 商店页**：`https://store.steampowered.com/app/2297040/`\n- **价格状态**：目前游戏显示为 **“未发布 / 即将推出”（Unreleased）**，Steam 页面提示可添加至愿望单以便发售时收到通知。搜索结果中**暂未显示具体售价**。\n\n## 2. 截图与视觉内容\nSteam 商店页面已上传多张截图和宣传图，主要包括：\n- **默认角色预览图**：一张 AI 生成的角色概念图（官方注明为“粗略影像，最终成品会有所不同”）。角色设定为**白丝洛丽塔、白毛粉瞳的萝莉猫娘**，动态立绘，并带有**好感度系统**。\n- **实际游戏截图**：页面包含多张标注为“截图 #4”、“截图 #5”等商店截图，以及名为 `kailu.jpg` 的展示图，展示了桌面宠物在实际桌面环境中的效果。\n\n## 3. “官网”与项目来源\n- **没有独立的官方网站**。当前的主要官方页面即为 **Steam 商店页**。\n- 该项目衍生自另一个免费的 GitHub 开源项目：**《碧蓝航线秘书舰》**（Azur Lane Secretary）。\n- 开发者社区与联系方式：\n  - **Bilibili**：@月夜Crescent\n  - **QQ 群**：515079733\n\n## 4. 核心功能简介\n- **高度自定义**：支持立绘、Spine 骨骼动画、精灵动画；可自定义行为、语音、音效、着色器（Shader）。\n- **创意工坊**：直接通过 **Steam 创意工坊（Steam Workshop）** 下载其他玩家分享的桌面宠物。\n- **事件交互**：支持与玩家的点击/按键交互、系统时间检测（例如深夜提醒睡觉或自动关机）等。\n- **行为编辑**：内置一套极简的“编程语言”，无需编程基础即可通过变量（如“好感度”）控制宠物在不同情境下的行为反应（例如按 WASD 行走、播放对应动画与音频）。\n\n## 5. 配置需求（参考）\n- **系统**：Windows 10\n- **CPU**：Intel Core i5-12400T（最低）\n- **内存**：4 GB RAM\n- **存储**：100 MB 可用空间\n\n总结来说，这是一款由 **月夜Crescent** 开发、主打二次元高度自定义的桌面宠物软件，目前尚未在 Steam 正式发售，暂无公开定价，具体发售时间可关注其 Steam 商店页或 Bilibili/QQ 群。\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a7ea36f8-8a00-489a-a31a-2a25ae00ed9a","uuid":"870894e6-1c57-49c2-98fd-80f359cba433","timestamp":"2026-05-21T16:29:29.176Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Custom Desktop Pet 自定义桌面宠物 Steam 价格 截图 官网 月夜Crescent","results":["Search results for query: Custom Desktop Pet Steam price Custom Desktop Pet screenshot Custom Desktop Pet official website",{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_d87j54pjj5k0u6v6s2h0","content":[{"title":"Recommandé - Produits similaires - Custom Desktop Pet-自定义桌面宠物","url":"https://store.steampowered.com/recommended/morelike/app/2297040/?l=french&snr=1_300_morelikev2__105"},{"title":"Recommended - Similar items - Custom Desktop Pet-自定义桌面宠物","