{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"tool_nCOleWLuD4fVKWFGIm8gnAwd","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"\"Custom Desktop Pet\" Steam appid 2297040 release date price tags features description\"\n\nSearch results for query: Custom Desktop Pet Steam appid 2297040 release date Custom Desktop Pet Steam price tags Custom Desktop Pet features description\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Custom Desktop Pet-自定义桌面宠物\",\"url\":\"https://isthereanydeal.com/product/018d9386-4606-71fa-bce5-b60eb307c0ce/\"},{\"title\":\"Custom Desktop Pet - Related apps\",\"url\":\"https://steamdb.info/app/2297040/linked/\"},{\"title\":\"Custom Desktop Pet-自定义桌面宠物\",\"url\":\"https://steambase.io/games/custom-desktop-pet-%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E6%A1%8C%E9%9D%A2%E5%AE%A0%E7%89%A9/info\"},{\"title\":\"Custom Desktop Pet-自定义桌面宠物\",\"url\":\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/2297040/Custom_Desktop_Pet/\"},{\"title\":\"Custom Desktop Pet-自定义桌面宠物 – Stats on Steam\",\"url\":\"https://games-stats.com/steam/game/custom-desktop-pet-zi-ding-yi-zhuo-mian-chong-wu/\"},{\"title\":\"Custom Desktop Pet-自定义桌面宠物\",\"url\":\"https://isthereanydeal.com/steam/app/2297040/\"}]\n\nBased on the web search results for **Custom Desktop Pet** (Steam AppID **2297040**), here is the information available:\n\n### Basic Info\n| Attribute | Details |\n|-----------|---------|\n| **App ID** | 2297040 |\n| **Title** | Custom Desktop Pet-自定义桌面宠物 |\n| **Developer** | 月夜Crescent |\n| **Publisher** | 月夜Crescent / 春江花月夜-ac |\n| **Platform** | Windows |\n| **Status** | **Coming Soon** (Unreleased) |\n\n### Release Date\n**Not yet released.** The Steam store page and SteamDB list the game as **\"Coming soon\"** with no official release date announced. Third-party tracker data shows placeholder/pre-order entries but no confirmed launch date.\n\n### Price\n**Not announced.** As the game has not been released, no pricing information is currently available on the Steam store or authorized retailers.\n\n### Tags / Genres\n- Indie\n- Casual\n- **Steam Workshop**\n- Single-player\n- Family Sharing\n- Desktop Pet\n- Customization\n\n### Key Features\n- **Deep Customization**: Create your own desktop pet using custom assets (painting, Spine animation, and sprite animation).\n- **Steam Workshop**: Download and share desktop pets created by other users.\n- **Behavior Scripting**: Customize pet behavior, voice, sound effects, and shaders using a simple built-in \"programming language\" (no coding experience required).\n- **Event Interactions**: Set up reactions to different inputs, time-based events (e.g., late-night reminders), and key presses (e.g., WASD movement with animations).\n- **Dynamic Animations**: Includes a default AI-generated character with dynamic animations out of the box.\n\n### Description\n> This is a desktop pet that supports customization, supports painting, spine, and sprite animation. There are also event interactions, and other interesting functions. You can use the assets to make your own desktop pet, and customize its behavior, voice, sound effects, shader, etc. Of course, you can also directly download desktop pets shared by others through the Steam Workshop.\n>\n> The attached e-book explains in detail how to organize asset files and customize your pet. You can define variables (like a \"favorability level\"), control animations/audio with key presses, detect system time, and even create shutdown reminders. Using the provided functions, you can create a personalized pet that suits your preferences.\n\n**Source**: [Steam Store Page](https://store.steampowered.com/app/2297040/Custom_Desktop_Pet/), SteamDB, Steambase, IsThereAnyDeal\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a7ea36f8-8a00-489a-a31a-2a25ae00ed9a","uuid":"cd3b1262-f6c6-426f-8084-5e244598605c","timestamp":"2026-05-21T16:31:04.112Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"\"